<item>
            <title>[LU-13355] adler32 wrapper in libcfs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13355</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;libcfs has wrappers in order to be able to use adler32 as any other crypto module. But libcfs should not be considered as the owner of this implementation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="58343">LU-13355</key>
            <summary>adler32 wrapper in libcfs</summary>
